contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|PSU}} The initials '''PSU''' often refer to a [[power supply]] unit, [[Power supply unit (computer)|often that of a computer]]. '''PSU''' may also refer to: '''Universities''': *[[Pennsylvania State University]] *[[Portland State University]] *[[Pangasinan State University]] *[[Palawan State University]] *[[Partido State University]] *[[Plymouth State University]] *[[Pittsburg State University]] *[[Plattsburgh State University]] *[[Pembroke State University]] *[[Prince of Songkla University]] *[[Prince Sultan University]] *[[Puntland State University]] *[[Pacific States University]] In '''entertainment''': *[[Public Surveillance Unit]], fictional law enforcement organisation in the ''Judge Dredd'' comic strip *[[Phantasy Star Universe]], a persistent ORPG game by SEGA for PlayStation 2, Xbox 360 and PC *[[PSU.com]], PlayStation Universe website In '''mathematics''': *Projective Special Unitary group - a mathematics [[Projective_unitary_group#Projective_special_unitary_group|projective unitary group]] In '''oceanography''': *Practical salinity unit, a unit for quantifying a fluid's [[salinity]] Other Uses: *[[Parti Socialiste Unifié (disambiguation)]], various organizations in countries where French is often used *[[Passenger service unit]] *[[Police Support Unit]] *[[Port Security Unit]], a U.S. Coast Guard expeditionary force protection unit. *[[Practical salinity unit]] *[[Prueba de Selección Universitaria]], public university admission test in Chile *[[Public Sector Undertaking]], an Indian company with majority government ownership *[[Post-Soviet Union]], i.e. [[CIS]] {{disambiguation}}
